      "en": "Practical information about Walibi"
    },
    "content": {
      "_type": "localeText",
      "nl": "Walibi Holland ligt in Biddinghuizen en staat bekend om spectaculaire achtbanen zoals Untamed en Goliath.",
      "en": "Walibi Holland is located in Biddinghuizen and is famous for roller coasters like Untamed and Goliath."
    },
